snippet.title: Erenshor Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Erenshor on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2382520/Erenshor/
Play the Demo! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2522260/Erenshor_Demo/
Join the Discord! https://discord.gg/M2ynUdcNT7

Erenshor is a single player, simulated MMORPG where you play online with 100+ "SimPlayers" who will adventure, quest, and fight along side you. 

MMORPG Gameplay, at your own pace.
